description:
Update web board to display and view attachments.

## Changes

### 1. Tick Card (tick-card.ts)

Add attachment indicator badge when tick has attachments:
```html
<span class="meta-badge attachments">ðŸ“Ž 2</span>
```

Styled similar to other meta badges.

### 2. Detail Drawer (tick-detail-drawer.ts)

Add attachments section with thumbnail grid:

```html
<div class="attachments-section">
  <h4>Attachments</h4>
  <div class="attachment-grid">
    <div class="attachment-thumb" @click=${openLightbox}>
      <img src="${attachment.url}" alt="${attachment.description}" />
      <span class="attachment-label">${attachment.filename}</span>
    </div>
    ...
  </div>
</div>
```

### 3. Lightbox Modal

On thumbnail click, open full-size image in modal:
- Dark overlay
- Centered image (max 90vw x 90vh)
- Close on click outside or Escape
- Navigation arrows if multiple attachments
- Caption showing description/filename

### Styling

```css
.attachment-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr));
  gap: 0.5rem;
}

.attachment-thumb {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.attachment-thumb img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
```

### API

Attachments already in tick data from /api/ticks endpoint.
No new API needed - just render existing attachment URLs.
